{
  "stem": "16.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I had this-- it wasn't a classmate of mine, but somebody from my hometown.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he jumped in and wanted to-- and Germans are holding you back with the machine gun.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Stand back!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Stand back!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That water is contaminated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Most of them didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They didn't speak German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I understood what they're-- what they're yelling about.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And anyway, he made it to the water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he started drinking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one German said, [SPEAKING GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You want water?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Here, have some.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he held his head down till he drowned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is-- comes back to me as a nightmare many times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And another time-- this was a, a good friend from my hometown.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was in the dream myself, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Although one time, I must have been moaning because my wife woke me up and said, you had a bad dream.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I immediately realized what the-- I, I knew what the dream-- what I was dreaming about.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, not every night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But I, I, I have it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It comes back, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I did tell it to-- then I have to go back to when I arrived to New York, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's another story in itself, which I will-- I will come to if you're interested.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just want to finish this story because what happened is this was a bitter cold winter, a lot of snow-- knee-deep in many areas.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was difficult to march, to walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yet the last row had it always the worst because you always heard a shot, and maybe 10 minutes later, another shot.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So later on, you found out, because pretty soon, the ones that were in last row, they ran forward.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
